1 TITL Descendants of Hermannus Kreutzjans
1 AUTH George H. Kreutzjans, P.E.
1 NOTE This was a family tree created by George Kreutzjans. It is written in a mix of German and English. It outlines all of the found descendants of Hermannus Kreutzjans(1783-1860). Much of the Marriage dat
2 CONC a is from Mariä Himmelfahrt. Other data is presumed from church birth and death records.
